	<div style="text-align:right;">
		CARVALHO, Manoella Ribas<sup>1</sup>; SILVEIRA, Joana Léa Meira<sup>2</sup>; LIMA, Nery Nishimura de<sup>3</sup>; LUCYSZYN, Neoli<sup>4</sup>		<BR>
